OL,5, A man who was charged #500 for a short 
OL,6, pedicab trip in central London is      
OL,7, calling for the cabs to be regulated.  
OL,9,FThe tourist said he was "distracted" by
OL,10,Fthe driver when he made a card payment 
OL,11,Ffor the 10-minute journey on 29 July.  
OL,13,FHe later realised #500 had been taken  
OL,14,Ffrom his account by the driver straight
OL,15,Fafter the ride from Mayfair to Soho.   
OL,17,FCurrently, pedicab drivers may operate 
OL,18,Fwithout a licence and set their own    
OL,19,Fprices. However, the government has    
OL,20,Fsaid new laws will be introduced.      
